CatDescriptText: Mrs. Constance Smith's sons are Dalton and Ernie Smith, and daughters Mary Smith and Edythe Smith Perkins.
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of women, men, and children, including Dalton Smith standing third from left, Ernie Smith fifth from left, Mrs. Constance Smith seventh from left, and Mary Smith second from right, standing behind table with flowers, candles, and wrapped gifts, for honorary celebration of Constance Smith by Ebenezer Baptist Church Missionary Group, in interior of Ebenezer Baptist Church
